6. PROHIBITED USES:
   The following uses of this software are strictly prohibited:

   a) Using this software to bypass FRP or any theft protection
      on devices the user does not legally own.

   b) Offering paid "FRP unlock", "phone unlocking", or similar
      commercial services using this software.

   c) Processing devices through a commercial repair/unlock
      business without verifying the customer's legal ownership.

   d) Modifying or repackaging this software to remove or obscure
      anti-misuse warnings, ownership checks, or legal disclaimers.

   e) Distributing this software through channels primarily
      serving device theft (forums, groups, or services dedicated
      to unlocking stolen phones).

   f) Using this software on devices subject to law enforcement
      holds, court orders, or active theft investigations.

